Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# When I Close My Eyes 当我闭上双眼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当我闭上双眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我听见。\NI hear things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,马车经过时，它的轮子\NThe sound of a carriage passing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟鹅卵石路撞出的声音。\Nas its wheels wobble against the cobblestone paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我淡出于包裹著我的人群的嘈杂声。\NI fade softly against the murmurs of the crowds that encompass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,风铃明明被狂风吹著，\NWooden chimes are faintly heard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,却没人听的到它的声音。\Nagainst the howling wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不清。\NUnknown to me.
Comment: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当我闭上双眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见。\NI see things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见她，笑著回头看我，\NI see her smiling back at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我记忆中的那样，\Njust like I remembered her doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是多么遥远，当时事情还没这么复杂。\Nlong ago when things were simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见我，在镜子里面，\NI see myself in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上作梦时，我知道镜子里的是我，\NIn my dreams, I know it's me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,白天醒著时，我却是开始怀疑自己。\Nbut in the daylight, I can never be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,艳丽的青与赤在天上飞舞，但老实说，再怎么美丽，\NBrilliant blues and pinks cascade across a sky that, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我都从没抬头看过。\NI never look up at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好特别的。\NThis is nothing profound.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,当我闭上双眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我梦见。\NI dream of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们只不过\NBut they're only familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,仅只于\Nto the point
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中\Nof a feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,的感受。\Nthat I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我闭上双眼，\NI close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在花凋叶落前我都不要醒来。\Nand dream until every petal falls.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,## 尾奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当我闭上双眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我试著忘记张眼时的感觉。\NI try to forget what it's like to keep them open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当我闭上双眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我试著忘记他们的责骂。\NI try to forget the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,当我闭上双眼，\NWhen I close my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我试著记好我的名字。\NI try to remember my name.
